SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1778691955
OL,3,C'I want women to feel safer': using AI
OL,4,Cto fight predatory behaviour
OL,6,FA woman who was sexually assaulted
OL,7,Fwhen she was 12 is now part of a team
OL,8,Ftrying to use AI to make women safer
OL,9,Fin public spaces.
OL,11,FCockermouth-based Createc plans to use
OL,12,Flidar sensors, which can track
OL,13,Fpeople's movements and map them out as
OL,14,Fthese dots on a screen, to create
OL,15,Falerts if its 'Situate' system detects
OL,16,Fsomething that could be suspicious.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
