FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1778691955
OL,3,C'I want women to feel safer': using AI
OL,4,Cto fight predatory behaviour
OL,6,FRosie Richardson, Product and Strategy
OL,7,FDirector at Createc, says her
OL,8,Fexperience of being sexually assaulted
OL,9,Fwhen she was 12 has motivated her to
OL,10,Fmake women safer.
OL,12,FRosie has waived her right to
OL,13,Fanonymity to share her story with ITV
OL,14,FBorder.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1778691955
OL,3,C'I want women to feel safer': using AI
OL,4,Cto fight predatory behaviour
OL,6,FShe said: "When I was 12 years old, I
OL,7,Fwas a spectator at the Tour de France
OL,8,Fin Paris, and I was in a crowd, and
OL,9,Fthere was a horrible man walking
OL,10,Fthrough the crowd and just sexually
OL,11,Fassaulting people in the crowd, and
OL,12,Fthat happened to me.
OL,14,F"I think that happening to me at such
OL,15,Fa young age strikes a chord around
OL,16,Fjust how unsafe you are as a woman in
OL,17,Fpublic spaces, and just how little
OL,18,Fpeople will protect you even as a
OL,19,Fchild."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1778691955
OL,3,C'I want women to feel safer': using AI
OL,4,Cto fight predatory behaviour
OL,6,FRosie said the man's behaviour would
OL,7,Fbe detected with Createc's technology.
OL,9,F"They were walking through the crowd
OL,10,Fand deliberately sexually assaulting
OL,11,Fpeople as they went, and people were
OL,12,Fmoving away from them, and it's really
OL,13,Ftough to see that from the ground as a
OL,14,Fsecurity operative, so we're
OL,15,Fdeveloping something that would
OL,16,Fsupport people like me to have a trail
OL,17,Fof evidence and to have an alert that
OL,18,Fsomething might be going on in the
OL,19,Fcrowd that you might want to look at."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1778691955
OL,3,C'I want women to feel safer': using AI
OL,4,Cto fight predatory behaviour
OL,6,F"I want women to feel safer, and I've
OL,7,Fbeen really amazed by how many women
OL,8,Fhave told me that kind of thing would
OL,9,Fmake them feel safer.
OL,11,F"You get taught at a very young age to
OL,12,Fcarry your keys in between your
OL,13,Ffingers when you walk home at night -
OL,14,Fwhy don't we just put some tools in
OL,15,Fplace that can help support women and
OL,16,Fdeter men?"
OL,18,FRosie points out that the system she
OL,19,Fhas helped develop protects privacy,
OL,20,Fand does not rely on the software to
OL,21,Fmake any decisions itself.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1778691955
OL,3,C'I want women to feel safer': using AI
OL,4,Cto fight predatory behaviour
OL,6,FShe said: "Our system doesn't use any
OL,7,Fcameras at all. We are looking for
OL,8,Fpatterns of movement and behaviour,
OL,9,Fand we don't trigger any decisions.
OL,11,F"Everything we do is completely
OL,12,Fanonymised, and we're looking for
OL,13,Fthose patterns of behaviour that might
OL,14,Findicate something is wrong.
OL,16,F"It's then down to the person managing
OL,17,Fthe space to decide whether there is a
OL,18,Fthreat there or not.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1778691955
OL,3,C'I want women to feel safer': using AI
OL,4,Cto fight predatory behaviour
OL,6,F"I don't want to live in a world where
OL,7,Fmy face is kept on record everywhere,
OL,8,Fand whilst we want to protect people
OL,9,Fwe don't want to compromise on our
OL,10,Fprivacy and we shouldn't have to."
OL,12,FJoe Moore, a senior software developer
OL,13,Fat Createc, explained how the system
OL,14,Fworks.
OL,16,FHe told ITV Border: "Think about an
OL,17,Foperator sitting in a CCTV control
OL,18,Froom looking over 50 screens or 100
OL,19,Fcameras at once: it's an impossible
OL,20,Ftask, they're bound to miss something.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1778691955
OL,3,C'I want women to feel safer': using AI
OL,4,Cto fight predatory behaviour
OL,6,F"With lidar we're able to pinpoint
OL,7,Fwhere that is and what camera is
OL,8,Flooking at that area so we can have a
OL,9,Fcloser look at it.
OL,11,F"Think about something like stalking:
OL,12,Fone person is moving in a specific
OL,13,Farea and goes to a quieter area,
OL,14,Fsomeone pulls out of the crowd and
OL,15,Ffollows them, keeps a distance - that
OL,16,Fis suspicious behaviour, whether it's
OL,17,Factually a risk or not is not the
OL,18,Fconcern, it's having direction to see
OL,19,Fif we should have a look at it."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1778691955
OL,3,C'I want women to feel safer': using AI
OL,4,Cto fight predatory behaviour
OL,6,FThe latest Crime Survey for England
OL,7,Fand Wales estimated 15.9% of people
OL,8,Faged 16 and over had experienced
OL,9,Fsexual assault since the age of 16 -
OL,10,Fequivalent to 7.7 million people.
OL,12,FThe technology is still being
OL,13,Ftrialled, but the hope is that it can
OL,14,Fsoon be rolled out and make public
OL,15,Fspaces feel safer.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
